{"tid":2126473,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"求救！養狗經驗人士入","createTime":"2020-07-27T00:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T14:35:06.000Z","uid":169960,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"bd6317f70136135b38ed9644c80838aaede53825","tid":2126473,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T00:55:33.000Z","msg":"狗仔領養咗1個幾月<br />\n一直都教唔識係欄入面小便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大便佢去啱地方 識係尿墊上面去<br />\n但小便一時時 有時會係尿墊隔離<br />\n有時會去啱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人話狗仔唔會係自己瞓覺嘅地方去大小便<br />\n佢會係自己張床小便<br />\n同埋瞓覺冇得跟我係房瞓會吠到天光<br />\n但又成日係房地墊同床小便<br />\n今朝仲係我瞓緊覺嘅時候尿尿<br />\n成身都濕晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟點解會咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0331d65adabf0cd17ec8df74237e8449e047ed84","tid":2126473,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T00:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22086e5a07578cb90b5e9df8d2d668a07ca5d0a2","tid":2126473,"uid":282362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd6317f70136135b38ed9644c80838aaede53825","tid":2126473,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T00:55:33.000Z","msg":"狗仔領養咗1個幾月<br />\n一直都教唔識係欄入面小便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大便佢去啱地方 識係尿墊上面去<br />\n但小便一時時 有時會係尿墊隔離<br />\n有時會去啱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人話狗仔唔會係自己瞓覺嘅地方去大小便<br />\n佢會係自己張床小便<br />\n同埋瞓覺冇得跟我係房瞓會吠到天光<br />