己係尿墊上面痾屎"},{"pid":"bf27e9c59dc39b33c433077bd13f9231ae58e683","tid":2126473,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb4fbf203e7500c27bd26b895289e29aa00a9560","tid":2126473,"uid":215035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd6317f70136135b38ed9644c80838aaede53825","tid":2126473,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T00:55:33.000Z","msg":"狗仔領養咗1個幾月<br />\n一直都教唔識係欄入面小便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大便佢去啱地方 識係尿墊上面去<br />\n但小便一時時 有時會係尿墊隔離<br />\n有時會去啱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人話狗仔唔會係自己瞓覺嘅地方去大小便<br />\n佢會係自己張床小便<br />\n同埋瞓覺冇得跟我係房瞓會吠到天光<br />\n但又成日係房地墊同床小便<br />\n今朝仲係我瞓緊覺嘅時候尿尿<br />\n成身都濕晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟點解會咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:26:40.000Z","msg":"我隻狗就相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢一嚟我屋企就識係尿墊上面痾尿，但唔識係上面痾屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後我係佢痾過屎嘅地方都擺塊尿墊，過幾日佢就識自己係尿墊上面痾屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:35:10.000Z","msg":"我依家日日要洗三至四次床單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成張床褥都係尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dafa5132668ad03769593de2273e7dda11225ba","tid":2126473,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:40:59.000Z","msg":"放多d相是常識吧"},{"pid":"e22ee13ae94874704a59aabc6e4f349f6156c730","tid":2126473,"uid":294782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:44:22.000Z","msg":"佢冇安全感既, 你放件你著過未洗既衫去佢個竇度比佢, <br />\n佢個竇係點既? 洗下封一半, 搵野遮住蓋住唔好太開揚"},{"pid":"f6fe70b7953cf23808bfe510202bf71107f0f15c","tid":2126473,"uid":154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:45:17.000Z","msg":"似係分離焦慮<br />\n要慢慢教佢係尿墊痾，每次佢痾岩就做場大龍鳳讚佢(可獎野食)，痾錯就完全無視佢<br />\n夜晚要多d 起身抱佢去尿墊等佢自己痾，痾岩又大龍鳳<br />\n夜晚怕起唔到身就著狗尿片<br />\n最重要係教識佢獨立，唔好成日要痴人<br />\n<br />\nPs 我果隻之前都係咁，瀨尿瀨左兩年，最後教左大半年先教返繡"},{"pid":"0a85ed976a1a8c02d7557071c6dc517b8bb00db7","tid":2126473,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e22ee13ae94874704a59aabc6e4f349f6156c730","tid":2126473,"uid":294782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:44:22.000Z","msg":"佢冇安全感既, 你放件你著過未洗既衫去佢個竇度比佢, <br />\n佢個竇係點既? 洗下封一半, 搵野遮住蓋住唔好太開揚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:03:19.000Z","msg":"我有放<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢會係個陣瞓 但都會屙<br />\n搵嘢蓋住佢 佢會叫 <br />\n總之只要我係屋企但佢唔係痴住我就會叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5736e85c8c411dcd8c14c8987c0cbb90f10d46","tid":2126473,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6fe70b7953cf23808bfe510202bf71107f0f15c","tid":2126473,"uid":154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:45:17.000Z","msg":"似係分離焦慮<br />\n要慢慢教佢係尿墊痾，每次佢痾岩就做場大龍鳳讚佢(可獎野食)，痾錯就完全無視佢<br />\n夜晚要多d 起身抱佢去尿墊等佢自己痾，痾岩又大龍鳳<br />\n夜晚怕起唔到身就著狗尿片<br />\n最重要係教識佢獨立，唔好成日要痴人<br />\n<br />\nPs 我果隻之前都係咁，瀨尿瀨左兩年，最後教左大半年先教返繡"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:04:47.000Z","msg":"但我試過出門番工 睇cam佢又好地地<br />\n好少會係床屙尿<br />\n佢每次係床屙尿都係我係屋企嘅時候先會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b4550414870f91c83298f15b6e558c03419dcb","tid":2126473,"uid":169960,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9dafa5132668ad03769593de2273e7dda11225ba","tid":2126473,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:40:59.000Z","msg":"放多d相是常識吧"},"citedBy"